 ${misc:Depends},
 ${shlibs:Depends},
Suggests:
 kea-doc,
Description: DHCP Dynamic DNS service
 Kea is an IPv4 and IPv6 DHCP server developed by Internet Systems Consortium.
 .
 This package provides Dynamic DNS service to update DNS mapping based on
 DHCP lease events.

